@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

state StartChoice <<choice>>

StartChoice --> Login

state Login
Login : entry / getInfo
Login : do / verifyData
Login : exit / verified

state LoginDecision <<choice>>
Login --> LoginDecision

state "Valid Login" as ValidLogin
ValidLogin : entry / contain Info
ValidLogin : do / allow Access to system
ValidLogin : exit / farmEntry

state "Invalid Login" as InvalidLogin
InvalidLogin : entry / wrong Info
InvalidLogin : do / display Error message
InvalidLogin : exit / return To Start

LoginDecision --> ValidLogin
LoginDecision --> InvalidLogin

state farmEntry
farmEntry : entry / main area displayed
farmEntry : do / user chooses options
farmEntry : exit / showResults

state ShowMarketConditions
ShowMarketConditions : entry / user selects market conditions
ShowMarketConditions : do / display market conditions
ShowMarketConditions : exit / backToMain

state ShowMarketReport
ShowMarketReport : entry / user selects market report
ShowMarketReport : do / display market report
ShowMarketReport : exit / backToMain

state RequirePhoto
RequirePhoto : entry / user chooses pest control help
RequirePhoto : do / require photo
RequirePhoto : exit / showPestControlTechniques

state ShowPestControlTechniques
ShowPestControlTechniques : entry / user provides photo
ShowPestControlTechniques : do / display pest control techniques
ShowPestControlTechniques : exit / backToMain

state SoilSuggestions
SoilSuggestions : entry / receive soil information from user
SoilSuggestions : do / provide suggestions for suitable crops
SoilSuggestions : exit / backToMain

state WeatherInsights
WeatherInsights : entry / receive location from user
WeatherInsights : do / display weather insights
WeatherInsights : exit / backToMain

state LabourAvailability
LabourAvailability : entry / receive location from user
LabourAvailability : do / display labour availability details
LabourAvailability : exit / backToMain

state ContinueService
ContinueService : entry / user views results
ContinueService : do / allow users to continue using the service
ContinueService : exit / backToMain

state EndSession
EndSession : entry / user logs out
EndSession : do / end session
EndSession : exit / [*]

@enduml
